    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p><a href="http://framework.zend.com/developer/ticket/103">http://framework.zend.com/developer/ticket/103</a></p>

<p>Not all PHP installations have PDO support.</p>

<p>However, if available, the PDO adapter for MySQL should be used, since it offers better performance, the benefits of true prepared queries (no emulation required), and has more stable code than the MySQLi adapter.</p>

